The following packages in this repository are inspired by, modeled on, or
have call-site-compatible APIs with the equivalent ory/x package. The
implementations are original (clean-room rewrites against the standard
library) but the API shape and behaviour are aligned so consumers
familiar with ory/x see a familiar surface:

  - core/randstr        — modeled on ory/x/randx (rejection-sampled
                          random strings; uses crypto/rand.Int's
                          built-in rejection sampling rather than
                          ory's hand-rolled big.Int loop)
  - core/safecast       — modeled on ory/x/safecast (clamping
                          integer narrowing helpers; trivial 3-line
                          functions; extends with IntToInt32 and
                          IntToUint32)
  - httpx/urlutil       — modeled on ory/x/urlx (URL join/copy/parse
                          helpers; delegates to Go 1.19's
                          *url.URL.JoinPath rather than reimplementing
                          path joining)
  - httpx/pagination    — offset.go and link_header.go are modeled on
                          ory/x/pagination (RFC 5988 Link-header writer
                          and ?limit=&offset= parser; original
                          implementation, ory's API surface)

ory/x is Apache 2.0 licensed and rho-kit is also Apache 2.0 licensed,
